\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:11;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=130981\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:597:\"<p>Are you unhappy with the performance and ROI of your online shop? Don\'t get frustrated you are in the right place. In this article, we recommend you some awesome solutions to your problems. We also suggest you some best WooCommerce Plugins which are free. With our suggested tips, you can make an incredible online store. Think out [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account/130981/best-free-woocommerce-plugins/\">Best Free WooCommerce Plugins for Building Your Store</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Gobinda Tarafdar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28405:\"<p>Are you unhappy with the performance and <strong>ROI</strong> of your online shop? Don\'t get frustrated you are in the right place. In this article, we recommend you some awesome solutions to your problems. We also suggest you some <strong>best WooCommerce Plugins</strong> which are free. With our suggested tips, you can make an incredible online store.<span id=\"more-130981\"></span></p>\n<h2>Think out of the box</h2>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-146013\" src=\"https://wedevs.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2018/10/think-out-of-the-box.png\" alt=\"Think out of the box\" width=\"769\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/think-out-of-the-box.png 769w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/think-out-of-the-box-300x150.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/think-out-of-the-box-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to make an online store, you need to think slightly in a different way. While building a web store most of us just focus on the business process and earning money in a quick manner. Most of the cases we forget about the customer needs and demands. Becoming business-minded personnel is not a bad thing. We just want to give you a suggestion to avoid a common mistake.</p>\n<p>As a customer when you visit an online shop just think about the features which attract you most to stay on their site. Rather than ordering your desired product or service and jump back to other places on the internet. Our plan is to help you to build an attractive online shop of your own.</p>\n<h2>Features which going to help you in building an awesome WooCommerce Store</h2>\n<p>Are you started to think about the most attractive features of popular e-commerce sites?  To save your time we the team weDevs are sharing our study result with you. We categorized the feature list in two part.</p>\n<h3>Features for attracting the customers</h3>\n<p>In the first part, we share some features which give the <strong>customer a homely feel</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduce the wishlist feature to your customer.</li>\n<li>Product filtering facility.</li>\n<li>Product sliding feature.</li>\n<li>Sliding products categorically.</li>\n<li>Customized product tabs.</li>\n<li>Menu cart feature.</li>\n<li>Give your customer the freedom to choose their convenient delivery date.</li>\n<li>Enabling review features for customers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Essential features which help you to boost up your sale and manage your store</h3>\n<p>Following this second list which is obviously for <strong>boosting up your business</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Social login, commenting and sharing ability.</li>\n<li>Integration with google analytics.</li>\n<li>Conversion Tracker to track your customers anywhere.</li>\n<li>Product import and export facility.</li>\n<li>Speeding up your WooCommerce store.</li>\n<li>Enable backing up facility for your store.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>How to integrate these features in WooCommerce Store?</h2>\n<p>All the homework are done. Now it\'s time for sharing the way how will you add these valuable features to your online shop. Above mentioned features, can be easily availed by you in your web store through some Best WooCommerce Plugins.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-146026\" src=\"https://wedevs.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2018/10/Best-WooCommerce-Plugins.png\" alt=\"Best Woo-commerce Plugins\" width=\"769\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/Best-WooCommerce-Plugins.png 769w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/Best-WooCommerce-Plugins-300x150.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2018/10/Best-WooCommerce-Plugins-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\" /></p>\n<h3>WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin By <a href=\"https://templateinvaders.com/product/ti-woocommerce-wishlist-wordpress-plugin/?partner=Sabirah\">TemplateInvaders</a></h3>\n<p>WooCommerce Wishlist is one of the simplest to attract your customers and also helpful for making them a potential customer. It\'s quite possible for everyone to buy whatever they like, at that time if your site has the wishlist feature they can make a list of their desired products. When they capable to buy their desired product they will come again and buy from you.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ti-woocommerce-wishlist/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin</a> By TemplateInvaders is one of the best wishlist plugins. WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin is <strong>GDPR compliant</strong>. It has customized wishlist table columns like it shows unit prices, stock status, checkbox and so on.<br />\nIt has so many built-in features which sometimes maybe feels you that it\'s hazy. If any problem arises please take help from their support service.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"ti-woocommerce-wishlist\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4><strong>Alternatives to WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin</strong></h4>\n<p>You can give a try to other ones,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/?refer_id=1084066\" rel=\"noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</a> By YiThemes</li>\n<li>Wishlist WooCommerce By XootiX</li>\n<li>Wish List for WooCommerce By Algoritmika Ltd</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WooCommerce Products Filter By Realmag777</h3>\n<p>Enabling this feature on your site you will make your online store as a playground for the customers. They get a freedom of choice for whatever they want to do. According to team weDevs study, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-filter/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Products Filter</a> By Realmag777  is the best <strong>WooCommerce products filtering plugin for free</strong>. It has products searching by AJAX, dynamic products recount option, statistics, infinity scrolling and other amazing features.</p>\n<p>There have one drawback in the freemium package, if you want to add a feature of showing taxonomies/attributes like radio, checkbox, drop-down, multi-drop-down, radio buttons, Color, label, hierarchy drop-down, checkbox buttons in the drop-down in the search form, you have to avail their premium package.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"woocommerce-products-filter\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternatives to WooCommerce Products Filter Plugins</h4>\n<p>Besides that WooCommerce products filtering plugin, you can try another products filter plugins,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-product-filter/?refer_id=1084066\" rel=\"noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter</a> By YiThemes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/themify-wc-product-filter/\" rel=\"noopener\">Themify – WooCommerce Product Filter</a> By Themify</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Woocommerce Products Slider By Pickplugins</h3>\n<p>Product sliding feature makes your WooCommerce store very much lucrative and handy for the customers. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" rel=\"noopener\">Woocommerce Products Slider</a> By Pickplugins is one of the best <strong>Woocommerce Products Slider Plugins</strong>. You will get ultimate slide anywhere and also get <strong>auto slide player feature with mobile compatibility</strong>. Slider Stop on Hover, Slider Touch Drag, Mouse Drag, Custom speed for slider navigation & Pagination makes it a lucrative plugin.</p>\n<p>If you are not personally habituated with animated feature then this plugin may not be suitable for you. You can go with their flat theme.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"woocommerce-products-slider\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WooCommerce Product Sliding Plugins</h4>\n<p>Try these alternative freemium plugins if you are interested,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://shapedplugin.com/plugin/woocommerce-product-slider-pro/?ref=Sabirah\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Product Slider</a> By ShapedPlugin</li>\n<li>WooCommerce Product Slider By Subhansanjaya</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpb-woocommerce-product-slider/\" rel=\"noopener\">WPB WooCommerce Product Slider</a> By WPbean</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WP WooCommerce Category Slider By Pluginever</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woo-category-slider-by-pluginever/\" rel=\"noopener\">WP WooCommerce Category Slider</a> By Pluginever is another amazing plugin which helps you to show your product categorically. Many of us interested to see <strong>products categorical order</strong>. It\'s lightweight and fast loading plugin which helps you to take control of your product category.</p>\n<p>It has a limited number of themes in their freemium package. But other features are awesome to manage your product category.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"woo-category-slider-by-pluginever\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WooCommerce Sliding products categorically Plugins</h4>\n<p>Some alternatives also have for WooCommerce Sliding products categorically Plugins. You can try at your own interest,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woo-product-slider-and-carousel-with-category/\" rel=\"noopener\">Woo Product Slider and Carousel with category By WP Online Support</a></li>\n<li>WPB WooCommerce Category Slider By WPbean</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Custom Product Tabs for WooCommerce By YIKES</h3>\n<p>To make your online shop more attractive you can provide a customized products tab field in your store. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yikes-inc-easy-custom-woocommerce-product-tabs/\" rel=\"noopener\">Custom Product Tabs for WooCommerce</a> By YIKES, Inc is a wonderful plugin which helps you to avail that feature in your web store. <strong>It gives the privilege to add custom tabs to products</strong>. By creating saved tabs you can add them in multiple products later whenever you need.</p>\n<p>You can\'t add the saved tabs in bulk mood in their freemium package. That\'s a challenge, otherwise you can do your handful works with their freemium features.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"yikes-inc-easy-custom-woocommerce-product-tabs\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WooCommerce Customized Product Tabs Plugins</h4>\n<p>Try the other WooCommerce Customized Product Tabs Plugins if you want,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-custom-product-tabs-lite/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Custom Product Tabs Lite</a> By SkyVerge</li>\n<li>WebshopLogic\'s WooCommerce Custom Tabs</li>\n<li>WooCommerce Product Tabs By Nilambar Sharma</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WooCommerce Menu Cart By Jeremiah Prummer</h3>\n<p>Enabling cart feature in the menu bar will be added value at your online store. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-menu-cart/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Menu Cart</a> By Jeremiah Prummer, Ewout Fernhout plugin help you to create this feature in your online store.<strong> You can customize whatever you want to show in this menu cart bar</strong> by this WooCommerce Menu Cart plugin.</p>\n<p>In their freeware version, you will get a very few cart icon. To get more icon you have to purchase their premium features.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"wp-menu-cart\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WooCommerce Menu Cart Plugins</h4>\n<p>Regarding the above-mentioned plugin, you can try alternative one,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bew-menu-cart/\" rel=\"noopener\">BEW Menu Cart</a> By<a href=\"https://briefcasewp.com/?ref=13\"> BriefcaseWP</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Order Delivery Date for WooCommerce By Tyche Softwares</h3>\n<p>Giving privilege to customers regarding freedom to choose their convenient delivery date will add an extra value to your online shop\'s reliability. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/order-delivery-date-for-woocommerce/\" rel=\"noopener\">Order Delivery Date for WooCommerce</a> By Tyche Softwares is one of the best plugins for availing this feature.</p>\n<p>Order Delivery Date for WooCommerce will help to improve your customer satisfaction level. This WooCommerce Plugin <strong>gives customers a facility to select their convenient delivery date</strong>. Maybe a question hammering in your mind that if the customer gets the freedom to choose the delivery date, they can choose the date before the minimum requirement date to deliver the product. Don\'t worry about that, Order Delivery Date for WooCommerce By Tyche Softwares already provide the option in their feature. The Minimum required time for delivery can be set by you.</p>\n<p>You cannot enable or disable delivery date for specific product categories in their freemium package.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"order-delivery-date-for-woocommerce\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to Order Delivery Date for WooCommerce Plugins</h4>\n<p>There are other plugins which you can try at your own need,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/byconsole-woo-order-delivery-time/\" rel=\"noopener\">Woocommerce order delivery or pickup with date and time</a> By Console</li>\n<li>Dreamfox Media\'s Woocommerce Delivery Date</li>\n<li>Woocommerce Customer Delivery Date Time Selection By Raficsedu</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WP Product Review Lite By ThemeIsle</h3>\n<p>Collecting the customer reviews you can judge your product quality. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-product-review/\" rel=\"noopener\">WP Product Review Lite</a> By ThemeIsle is one of the best WooCommerce product review plugins. It\'s very easy to set up and it <strong>has a unique feature of the pros and cons list.</strong></p>\n<p>A little bit challenge in their free version that you will not get the shortcodes. To get these you just need to avail their premium package.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"wp-product-review\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WP Product Review Lite Plugins</h4>\n<p>Beside the WP Product Review Lite plugin, you can try other ones,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-review/\" rel=\"noopener\">Product Review</a> By Nazmul Ahsan</li>\n<li>Review & Product Review by Review Builder By Review Builder By Sygnoos</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now let\'s talk about some <strong>business growth</strong>. We know you are eagerly waiting for this section for a long time. This section is dedicated to your business growth. Hopefully, you will be benefited if you stay with us.</p>\n<h3>WordPress Social Share, Social Login, and Social Comments Plugin – Super Socializer By Team Heateor</h3>\n<p>By enabling this feature you can grow the attention of your customer. If they share your product this will become very big marketing for your online shop. That could bring more loyal customer to your online shop.</p>\n<p>To avail that feature you can try <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/super-socializer/\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress Social Share, Social Login, and Social Comments Plugin – Super Socializer</a> By Team Heateor which is one of the best WooCommerce plugins. By this plugin, you can provide awesome features like<strong> social login, facebook commenting and social sharing of your products.</strong></p>\n<p>The main drawback of this plugin is you cannot run this plugin in your localhost for testing purposes. You have to activate it in your live site.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"super-socializer\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WordPress Social Share, Social Login, and Social Comments Plugins</h4>\n<p>Some other plugins also some features like that one. You can try if needed,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-social-media-share-buttons/\" rel=\"noopener\">Woocommerce Social Media Share Buttons</a> By Toastie Studio</li>\n<li>ShareIt! Social Buttons By DefThemes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/social-networks-auto-poster-facebook-twitter-g/\" rel=\"noopener\">NextScripts: Social Networks Auto-Poster</a> By NextScripts</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Analytify – Google Analytics Dashboard Plugin for WordPress By Analytify</h3>\n<p>Google analytics helps you get the overview of how long the customer stays on your site, how many clicks they provide to you and many more.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-analytify/\" rel=\"noopener\">Analytify – Google Analytics Dashboard Plugin for WordPress</a> By Analytify can be the best solution for you to get the data of your WooCommerce store. This is one of the best woocommerce plugins which provide the data of total product view, product clicks, products remove from the cart, unique purchase transaction and many other relevant data for your online store. With these data, <strong>you can do remarketing of your products and online shop</strong>.</p>\n<p>There is challenge their woocommerce integration is for the premium package. But you can check their freemium features that\'s quite good enough.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"wp-analytify\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>The alternative to Analytify – Google Analytics Dashboard Plugin for WordPress plugin</h4>\n<p>There are other plugins in the marketplace, let\'s have a look,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Analytics for WordPress</a> By MonsterInsights</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Analytics Dashboard for WP</a> by ExactMetrics (formerly GADWP)</li>\n<li>WD Google Analytics – user-friendly Google Analytics integration plugin By WebDorado</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WooCommerce Conversion Tracking By Tareq Hasan</h3>\n<p>Most of the online shop owners run advertising campaigns for their online products. When you run an advertising campaign in several platforms they often get you several tracking codes and you have to incorporate these codes into your sites for tacking your visitors. In WooCommerce stores it\'s quite tough to track the behavior of customers in a right way.</p>\n<p>To reduce the hassle you can try <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-conversion-tracking/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Conversion Tracking</a> By Tareq Hasan. This is the only one unique solution to serve the purpose. With this best woocommerce plugin, <strong>you can collect customers behavioral data</strong> and send them to different Ad Platforms like Facebook, Twitter, Google Adwords. And use the data to <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/117901/woocommerce-retargeting-conversion-tracking/\" rel=\"noopener\">retarget your audiences</a>.</p>\n<p>One challenge minor challenge of that plugin is, if you want the perfect audience feature, you have to avail their premium service.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"woocommerce-conversion-tracking\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<p><strong>Sorry to say, there are no alternative plugins for WooCommerce Conversion Tracking Plugin.</strong></p>\n<p>These are enough for the boosting up your sale at the initial stage. Now we like to share some tips on WooCommerce <strong>Shop management</strong> issues which make your work easier.</p>\n<h3>Product Import Export for WooCommerce plugin by XAdapter</h3>\n<p>Importing and exporting the product is a very time being and boring task for every market owners. Every time you have to maintain the given CSV format of WooCommerce. To reduce the pain you can try <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" rel=\"noopener\">Product Import Export for WooCommerce plugin</a> by XAdapter. This plugin <strong>helps you to save the time and make the boring task very easy.</strong></p>\n<p>There is a challenge to upload variable and group products in their freemium package. To get that feature you have to avail their premium features.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"product-import-export-for-woo\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to Product Import Export for WooCommerce Plugins</h4>\n<p>Many plugins are available in the market, you can try,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-xml-csv-product-import/\" rel=\"noopener\">Import Products from any XML or CSV to WooCommerce</a> By Soflyy</li>\n<li>WooCommerce – Store Exporter By Visser Labs</li>\n<li>WOOEXIM – WooCommerce Export-Import Plugin By WOOEXIM.COM</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WooCommerce Speed Drain Repair By WP Fix</h3>\n<p>For several purposes, we activate several plugins in our WooCommerce Stores. Those plugins serve our purposes well but on another side, they make our site slow. Maybe you have the issue. if not, that\'s great.</p>\n<p>Those who are facing the site slower issue, don\'t worried about it. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wc-speed-drain-repair/\" rel=\"noopener\">WooCommerce Speed Drain Repair</a> By WP Fix maybe<strong> the best solution for boosting up your WooCommerce Store</strong> in the freemium package. This plugin stops the loading of other unwanted extra items in woocommerce.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"wc-speed-drain-repair\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>Alternative to WooCommerce Speed Drain Repair Plugin</h4>\n<p>Some speeding up plugins are available in the market, you can try one of these also,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/breeze/\" rel=\"noopener\">Breeze – WordPress Cache Plugin</a> By Cloudways</li>\n<li>WP Asset CleanUp (Page Speed Optimizer) By Gabriel Livan</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wp-rocket.me/\" rel=\"noopener\">WP-Rocket</a> By WP Rocket</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>WordPress Backup & Security Plugin – BlogVault By BlogVault</h3>\n<p>Backing up is the most essential task for every online store owners. Anytime anything can happen. We have to be prepared for every situation. If you backed up your site on regular basis you can fix any accidental issue within a few moments.</p>\n<p>For backing up your WooCommerce Store, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/blogvault-real-time-backup/\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress Backup & Security Plugin – BlogVault</a> By BlogVault is the best solution. <strong>They provide real-time backup service for your WooCommerce store.</strong> Your data will save at their BlogVault servers and on Amazon S3.</p>\n<p>WordPress Backup & Security Plugin – BlogVault also provides the <strong>security service for your WooCommerce Store.</strong></p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"blogvault-real-time-backup\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h4>The alternative to WordPress Backup & Security Plugin – BlogVault</h4>\n<p>There are other plugins for backing up the WordPress sites. You can give a look to those plugins,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/backwpup/\" rel=\"noopener\">BackWPup – WordPress Backup Plugin</a> By Inpsyde GmbH</li>\n<li>UpdraftPlus WordPress Backup Plugin By UpdraftPlus.Com, DavidAnderson</li>\n<li>Backup & Restore Dropbox By backup-dropbox</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Bonus Plugin</h3>\n<p>If you want to expand your business or having a<strong> plan to build a multivendor marketplace</strong> of your own by WooCommerce platform then you can start your business by our <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/dokan-lite/\" rel=\"noopener\">Dokan Multivendor Marketplace lite</a>. The Dokan Multivendor Marketplace lite is a freemium plugin. By Dokan, you can run a Multivendor marketplace business smoothly with its prebuilt awesome features and supports. It is one of <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/30625/best-woocommerce-multivendor-plugin/\" rel=\"noopener\">the best multivendor marketplace</a> plugins among all.</p>\n<p><div class=\"wp-pic-wrapper right large\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 20px;float: right; \"><div class=\"wp-pic large plugin wp-pic-ajax scheme1\"  id=\"download-sexion\"data-type=\"plugin\" data-slug=\"dokan-lite\" data-image=\"\" data-expiration=\"\"  data-layout=\"large\"  ><div class=\"wp-pic-body-loading\"><div class=\"signal\"></div></div></div></div><!-- .wp-pic-wrapper--></p>\n<h2><strong>Wrapping up</strong></h2>\n<p>Wooh, finally, we are at the end of our long discussion. If you follow the above-mentioned tips you will be benefitted. Our suggested best WooCommerce plugins are working fine in our environment as we full fill the minimum requirements of installation what are mentioned by them. Hence last but not the least tip for you, if you find any problem to activate or operate these plugins please take help from their support teams. A huge thanks from team weDevs for staying with us.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account/130981/best-free-woocommerce-plugins/\">Best Free WooCommerce Plugins for Building Your Store</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://wedevs.com/account/130981/best-free-woocommerce-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n   \n    \n        \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n                \n              \n    \n              \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Dokan Nails Prestigious FinancesOnline Award 2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://wedevs.com/145835/dokan-nails-financesonline-award-2018/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"